   <H1>Thomas B. Silver</H1>

</CENTER>

Thomas B. Silver holds the Ph.D. in Government from the Claremont Graduate School.  One of 
the founders of the Claremont Institute, Dr. Silver presently serves as Chief Deputy to Los 
Angeles County Supervisor Michael D. Antonovich.  He is the author of <i>Coolidge and the 
Historians</i> (Carolina Academic Press, 1982).  


