<HTML>
<TITLE> A Blueprint For Family Freedom </TITLE>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="/townhall/FRC/wash.gif" WIDTH=425
HEIGHT=125>
<H2> A Blueprint for Family Freedom</H2>

<P>
</CENTER>
<HR SIZE = 3 WIDTH = 50%><P>
<P>
<CENTER><H3> Table of Contents</H3></CENTER>

<UL TYPE = BALL ><A HREF = "#restoring"><B> Restoring the Sanctity of Human Life</B></A>
<UL TYPE = BALL ><LI>End Federally Funded Abortions
<LI>Prohibit D & X Abortions
<LI>Retain Forced Abortion Asylum Policy
<LI>Adopt the $5,000 Adoption Tax Credit
<LI>Coercive Abortion Training Threatens Accreditation of Hospitals
</UL><P>
<A HREF = "#empower"><B> Empower Parents for Education</B></A>	
<UL TYPE = BALL ><LI>Getting Back to the Basics:  Disestablishing the Education Department
<LI>Getting Back to the Basics:  Repealing Goals 2000
<LI>Promote Parental Choice in Education
</UL><P>
