<UL TYPE = BALL ><LI>Adopt the $500 Per-Child Tax Credit
<LI>Broaden IRA Eligibility to Non-Employed Spouses
<LI>Support Medical Savings Accounts</UL>
<P>
<A HREF = "#tame"><B> Tame the Cultural Wilderness</B></A>	
