<html><head>
<TITLE>Ben Boychuk</TITLE>
</head>

<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<center>

   <hr noshade>

   <A HREF = "../bios.htm">Return to Staff and Fellows</A> ||
   <A HREF = "../index.html">Claremont Institute Home Page</A>

   <hr noshade>

   <H1>Ben Boychuk</H1>

</CENTER>

<a href="mailto:bboychuk@aol.com">Ben Boychuk</a> is Director of Publications and editor of Precepts for the Claremont Institute. His writing has appeared in the <I>Los Angeles Times</I>, the <I>Washington Times</I>, the <I>San Diego Union-Tribune</I>, the L.A. <I>Daily News</I>, and the <I>Daily Oklahoman</I>.

Previously, he was Managing Editor of <I>The Report Card</I>, an education reform magazine published by the Center for the Study of Popular Culture.

He received a B.A. in Political Science from the University of California-San Diego in 1994. 

<P>

<CENTER>

   <hr noshade>

